    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sinopse</h2>&quot;Stages of Life&quot; is an <strong>exciting puzzle game</strong> that follows the life of a girl, showing <strong>moments from her childhood to her adult life.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/a9f79caaff6553b7a468f41beb7e61cb.poster.avif?t=1717081276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/a9f79caaff6553b7a468f41beb7e61cb.webm?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/a9f79caaff6553b7a468f41beb7e61cb.mp4?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience:</h2><br>Each level offers a new opportunity for <strong>reflection and learning</strong>, allowing the player to jointly <strong>experience the girl's moments</strong> in an authentic and empathetic way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/0af37e6770c0318043925bdc9dca1fcf.poster.avif?t=1717081276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/0af37e6770c0318043925bdc9dca1fcf.webm?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/0af37e6770c0318043925bdc9dca1fcf.mp4?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><br>The game has <strong>6 different scenarios</strong>, which the girl goes through during her timeline. The player will be able to select to assemble in the order they wish, in addition to being able to <strong>choose one of the different sizes</strong> available to assemble and <strong>choose the background color</strong> of their preference.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/7966895c903ad417f41eff633decdbf4.poster.avif?t=1717081276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/7966895c903ad417f41eff633decdbf4.webm?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/7966895c903ad417f41eff633decdbf4.mp4?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Original Graphics and Music:</h2><br>With colorful <strong>graphics and an inspiring soundtrack</strong>, “Stages of Life” is an engaging game that seeks to be <strong>casual and relaxing</strong>, ensuring that the player can complete challenges in a calm and enjoyable way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/339b4d1ac47b1f82970462ba40622f27.poster.avif?t=1717081276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/339b4d1ac47b1f82970462ba40622f27.webm?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/339b4d1ac47b1f82970462ba40622f27.mp4?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Objectives:</h2><br>The ultimate goal is to bring a <strong>relaxing environment to players</strong>, so they can forget about the stressful activities in life, as well as make them feel <strong>moved and inspired</strong> by the girl's story and her journey of overcoming challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/c9914afc990534e298e2fc62b4225479.poster.avif?t=1717081276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/c9914afc990534e298e2fc62b4225479.webm?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322170/extras/c9914afc990534e298e2fc62b4225479.mp4?t=1717081276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
